column2: SELECT TOP # gsi.z, gsl.neiii_#_reqw, gsl.h_beta_reqw, gsl.h_beta_reqw_err, gsl.oii_#_reqw, gsl.oii_#_reqw_err, gsl.nii_#_reqw, gsl.nii_#_reqw_err, gsl.h_alpha_reqw, gsl.h_alpha_reqw_err, p.objid, p.ra,p.dec,p.petror9#_r, p.dered_z, p.dered_r, p.dered_g   FROM Galaxy as p    JOIN galSpecLine AS gsl ON p.specobjid = gsl.specobjid    JOIN galSpecInfo As gsi ON p.specobjid = gsi.specobjid WHERE gsl.oii_#_reqw > # and gsl.h_beta_reqw > # and gsl.nii_#_reqw > # and gsl.h_alpha_reqw > #
